message:
Ahoy freshers and sophomores!

We are delighted by the number of people interested in the concept of an international exchange and have taken the first step towards going for one. To further the zeal, we are selecting our first batch of students for Global Volunteer 2017-18. 

If you dare to stand out amongst a crowd and dream of worlds beyond your boundaries, come meet us!

To know more and volunteer abroad, register here: bit.ly/GV_AIESEC and meet us at 
F-127, Main Building | Sat-Sun 2nd & 3rd Sept | 3-7 PM

Kick-start you international journey!

A completely different side of Egypt unraveled before our exchange participant Harsh Yadav as he traveled across 13 different cities. Check out his volunteering experience with Ain Sham's University as an intern for the project "Explore Egypt".

To volunteer abroad : bit.ly/GV_AIESEC

#ExchangeDiaries
#GlobalVolunteer2017
